    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver or a great project car for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a few small dents, and fading clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all electronics still function as intended. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need a suspension refresh and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that reflects its mileage and years on the road.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
